cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC. 

The paper focuses on activity recognition and spatio-temporal action localization using deep learning models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques to fuse information from different sources, which suggests a possible fit with cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of human activity knowledge, which could be related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper deals with video analysis, which could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia).
